721556f-a.title: Manhattan: Madison Street - Grand Street
721556f-a.text:
408 to 414 (3-story house with Burke Bros. sign on it) Madison Street,
south side, west of, adjoining and at its point of confluence with Grand
Street. Also shown are Nos. 575 to 581 (from 2-story house with sign
covering its second floor windows, leftward) Grand Street, south side, at,
adjoining and east of its point of confluence with Madison Street.
March 26, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
